### GET PRODUCT CATALOG
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products-catalog HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: "application/json"

{
    "page": 1,
    "size": 10
}

### GET PRODUCTS BY IDS
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: "application/json"

{
    "id_list": [10, 2, 3]
}

### CREATE NEW USER
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: "application/json"

{
    "username": "some_user2",
    "password": "12345678"
}

### DELETE USER
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: "application/json"

{
    "user_id": 9
}

### ADD MONEY TO USER
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/wallets HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: "application/json"

{
    "user_id": 18,
    "money_amount": 34000
}

### ADD PRODUCT TO USER BASKET
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/basket HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: "application/json"

{
    "user_id": 8,
    "product_id": 6
}

### CREATE ORDER FOR USER
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: "application/json"

{
    "user_id": 8
}

### PAY FOR ORDER
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: "application/json"

{
    "order_id": 10
}

### GET USER NOTIFICATIONS
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications?user_id=8&limit=20&offset=0 HTTP/1.1
